              "displayName": "Karthik Kambatla",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "yarn-2814-0.patch is a preview of what I was thinking. It removes RMFatalEvent* and associated code and cleans up a few other methods in the RM.\n\nThe dispatcher, I believe, can be moved to RMActiveServices. Will update the patch again post that investigation. \n\nWelcome any early feedback. ",
